<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Stock Sense</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/business-candle-stick-graph-chart-stock-market-investment_41981-866.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }

    .glass {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .glow-button {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #3b82f6, #6366f1);
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px #3b82f6;
    }

    .glow-button:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px #6366f1;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .animated-gradient {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #3b82f6, #6366f1);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      animation: slide 4s infinite alternate;
    }

    @keyframes slide {
      from {
        background-position: 0%;
      }
      to {
        background-position: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="text-gray-800">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen px-6">
    <div class="glass max-w-3xl w-full p-10 text-center">
      
     
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold animated-gradient mb-4">Stock Sense</h1>
    
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium mb-6">Smarter insights, better investing.</p>

   
      <p class="text-base text-gray-800 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Stock Sense is a platform that helps predict stock prices, analyze market sentiment, and assess risk.
        Built for traders and investors, it combines data and intelligence to make financial decisions smarter and faster.
      </p>

    
      <a href="/authentication" class="inline-block glow-button text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-xl transition transform duration-300">
        ðŸš€ Get Started
      </a>

    
      <p class="mt-10 text-sm text-gray-600">&copy; 2025 Stock Sense | Built for IIITM Gwalior Hackathon</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
